<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">24倍速算法，24与某数相乘时，如果这个数能被5整除，可先把这个数分解成5乘以“几”，再用120乘以这个“几”。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">24×(5×a)=24×5×a=120×a</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中5×a为乘数。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">24×35=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 24×35</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=24×5×7</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=120×7</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=840</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>